##############################################################################

Methodology :
Implement the EM forward backward algorithm to code break a cipher given some english data


Input: 

training-data
English data to learn the grammer

cipher
The cipher to find the decoding for

NO_ITERATIONS
The number of iterations to run EM for.


Output: 
Each iteration decoding result with the P(cipher) value. In the end we see the probabilities of the final substitution made for each letter.


To run the program use the following command:

python decipher.py training-data cipher NO_ITERATIONS > decoded_output
